    "body": "When the requested stage doesn't exist, `spack cd` changes directory to the user's home.  At least personally I would expect it to stay in the same directory in this case.\n\n```\nscogland at cab668 in /tmp/scogland/spack-stage/spack-stage-D1e76p\n$ cd ~/spack\n\nscogland at cab668 in ~/spack (e53571d...)\n$ spack cd gcc\n==> Error: Build directory does not exist yet. Run this to create it:\n  spack stage gcc\n\nscogland at cab668 in ~ (gem:32)\n$ pwd\n/g/g12/scogland\n```\n",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
